OL,3,CBare-knuckle boxer appears in court
OL,4,Cover 'grossly offensive' YouTube videos
OL,6,FA bare-knuckle boxer turned YouTuber
OL,7,Fhas appeared in court accused of
OL,8,Fposting racially aggravated comments
OL,9,Fon a podcast earlier this week.
OL,11,FDerek Heggie, known as "Decca", faces
OL,12,Fone charge which alleges that he
OL,13,Fposted two videos on YouTube in which
OL,14,Fhe made "grossly offensive comments".
OL,16,FThese include a reference to "grooming
OL,17,Fgangs".
OL,19,FIt is also alleged that the comments
OL,20,Fwere made "for the purpose of causing
OL,21,Fdistress or anxiety".
