OL,6,FHeggie, 40, from Carlisle is one of
OL,7,Fseveral men prosecuted across Cumbria
OL,8,Fin the wake of a police operation in
OL,9,Fresponse to potential planned
OL,10,Fdisorder, amid days of national unrest.
OL,12,FHe appeared at Carlisle's magistrates'
OL,13,Fcourt in front of a district judge and
OL,14,Fpleaded not guilty to the charge.
OL,16,FProsecutor George Shelley alleged that
OL,17,Fthere had been "deliberate posts" on a
OL,18,FYouTube podcast.
