OL,3,CBare-knuckle boxer appears in court
OL,4,Cover 'grossly offensive' YouTube videos
OL,6,FMr Shelley alleged the comments were
OL,7,F"particularly inflammatory" in the
OL,8,Fcontext of disturbances taking place
OL,9,Facross the UK.
OL,11,FThe court heard that Heggie had
OL,12,Fportrayed himself as a journalist and
OL,13,Fmaintained that the online posts were
OL,14,Fjustified.
OL,16,FAfter hearing submissions, district
OL,17,Fjudge John McGarva sent the case to
OL,18,FCarlisle Crown Court.
